<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3152942" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="1"><link href="text/shared/01/01010304.xhp" name="Business">Business</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3151097" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2"><ahelp hid="">Contains contact information for business cards that use a layout from a 'Business Card, Work' category. Business card layouts are selected on the <emph>Business Cards</emph> tab.</ahelp></paragraph>
</section>
